  {
    "username": "tobi",
    "displayName": "@JCCFCanada",
    "text": "The term \"metadata\" appears only once in the 74-page Bill C-22. Without defining \"metadata,\" the Bill grants government power to order companies to retain Canadians' metadata for up to six months. The Criminal Code defines \"transmission data.\" It does not define the broader term ",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/JCCFCanada/status/2068038653251825684#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-19 18:30 UTC",
    "isRetweet": true,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "OpenAI",
    "displayName": "@OpenAI",
    "text": "This is an early step toward more robustly beneficial and aligned models: training models to carry beneficial traits into new situations, so as AI becomes more capable, it also becomes more reliable, transparent, and helpful for people.",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/OpenAI/status/2067722696759329125#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-18 21:34 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "OpenAI",
    "displayName": "@OpenAI",
    "text": "We also tested whether alignment persisted under pressure. ",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/OpenAI/status/2067722695270334549#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-18 21:34 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "OpenAI",
    "displayName": "@OpenAI",
    "text": "The most interesting test was cross-domain transfer.",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/OpenAI/status/2067722693714338044#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-18 21:34 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "OpenAI",
    "displayName": "@OpenAI",
    "text": "A small amount of this data produced broad gains beyond the training scenarios.",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/OpenAI/status/2067722691675824637#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-18 21:34 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "OpenAI",
    "displayName": "@OpenAI",
    "text": "We trained models with reinforcement learning on realistic conversations to reinforce beneficial traits like truthfulness, humility under uncertainty, openness to correction, fairness, and concern for human welfare, across 12 domains, including health, science, and education.",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/OpenAI/status/2067722689515856262#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-18 21:34 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "AnthropicAI",
    "displayName": "@AnthropicAI",
    "text": "Watch the robodogs in action in our first Project Fetch experiment:",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/AnthropicAI/status/2067651700757086553#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-18 16:52 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "AnthropicAI",
    "displayName": "@AnthropicAI",
    "text": "New Frontier Red Team blog: Phase 2 of Project Fetch, where we test how well Claude can program a robodog.",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/AnthropicAI/status/2067651699486200091#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-18 16:52 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "AnthropicAI",
    "displayName": "@AnthropicAI",
    "text": "These and other measures will allow us to track consequential shifts in the nature of work as they happen\u2014we'll incorporate some of them into the Anthropic Economic Index going forward. ",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/AnthropicAI/status/2066969542010806561#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-16 19:41 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "AnthropicAI",
    "displayName": "@AnthropicAI",
    "text": "Domain experts\u2014as judged by the questions they ask and vocabulary they use about a subject\u2014are more likely to see success.",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/AnthropicAI/status/2066969540412780644#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-16 19:41 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "AnthropicAI",
    "displayName": "@AnthropicAI",
    "text": "We compared Claude Code success rates between occupations. ",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/AnthropicAI/status/2066969538193920307#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-16 19:41 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "AnthropicAI",
    "displayName": "@AnthropicAI",
    "text": "The average task in Claude Code has grown more valuable.",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/AnthropicAI/status/2066969536423985295#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-16 19:41 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "AnthropicAI",
    "displayName": "@AnthropicAI",
    "text": "Using our privacy-preserving analysis tool, we analyzed 400K sessions from between October 2025 and April 2026.",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/AnthropicAI/status/2066969534322688427#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-16 19:41 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
  {
    "username": "AnthropicAI",
    "displayName": "@AnthropicAI",
    "text": "Our latest economic research introduces a framework for tracking Claude Code as it scales. ",
    "link": "https://nitter.net/AnthropicAI/status/2066969532380721386#m",
    "publishedAt": "2026-06-16 19:41 UTC",
    "isRetweet": false,
    "avatar": "https://nitter.net/pic/pbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2Fdefault_profile_normal.png"
  },
